Package: instax-scanner
Version: 1.0.2
Section: graphics
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Installed-Size: 137
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-gi, python3-opencv | python3-cv2, gir1.2-gtk-3.0
Recommends: python3-numpy
Maintainer: Instax Scanner <instax-scanner@localhost>
Description: Extract Instax photos from flatbed scanner scans
 Instax Scanner provides a graphical interface to automatically
 detect and extract individual Instax Mini, Square, and Wide photos
 from a multi-photo flatbed scanner scan (JPEG, PNG, TIFF).
 .
 Features:
  - Supports Mini (62x46mm), Square (62x62mm), and Wide (99x62mm) formats
  - Produces a tight crop and a full-card bordered crop per photo
  - Auto-detects scan DPI; handles any rotation and touching photos
  - Batch-process multiple scan files at once
